\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12191358\charrsid8598525 Liberal}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14574712\charrsid8598525 
, in these days, there were only the tow - parties. The Labour were just coming up, the same as the Communists are coming up now.
