No, well no, used to - you - you just - you just went by you're your father and mother - vote for Gullen, that was the Liberal - candidate at the time, Gullen, there was - there were a - who was the Conservative then, I don't know. Can't remember
. Oh no, you werena so - interested. The world wasn't in the state it's in now.
