What about the divisions up the way as well? Obviously there were people who had a lot more money
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11304503 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14574712\charrsid8598525 
Oh yes, there was people had a lot more money, in fact there was - these mill owners, they had plenty of money, they - but - I don't know - they say it was sweated labour but I don't know, people were happy. They didn't bother.
