I never was. But in some places mind - I've heard the people say have - if you were in
 private service you had to bow to the lady and the gentleman, my mother said, I'll never bow to any of them. She was - father says, you'll never make a - a - a - a something - a wife for a big house. She says, no. Why? She says. She says, they may be a w
e
e bit more money than we but they're just the same. Oh no, she never - done anything like that. You know - that there was people with more money that you but - it didn't trouble you, it didn't - nowadays if you - they're all - I want more money, ah well y
ou're getting it, I want it too.
