No. No. No. I - I don't know, through my life I - always seemed to get - be comfortable. Never had to go without. Don't ever remember ever having to go without. Of course - maybe I was fortuna
te, there was unfortunate people that had no money coming in at all, now my father never was out of work. You see. Even the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16721817 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14574712\charrsid8598525 How did you feel about these worse off folk?
